# Click Game

A very simple beginner-friendly web project built using basic HTML and JavaScript.  
The game increases a counter every time the user clicks a button.

# Features
- Click button to increase count
- Reset button to set count back to zero
- Uses only basic HTML and JavaScript
- No external libraries

# Technologies Used
- HTML
- JavaScript

# How to Run the Project
1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open the `click-counter.html` file in any web browser
3. Click the **Click Me** button to increase the count
4. Click **Reset** to reset the counter

